1.	Grade List > modify this view 
2.	 first sort by the column : Student account 
3.	choose show items only when the following is true 
4.	show the items when column : student account > is equal to > [Me]
5.	and then choose OR  > When coloumn :Graded by > is equal to > [Me] 
6.	click OK 
7.	go to Site contents > GradeList Settings > save list as template 
8.	enter the name and name template 
9.	click OK 
10.	go to class A > Site content > add an app > Grade List template that u just created 
11.	give it a name ( grade list class A ) 
